      "MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|4492,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|194000,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|32592,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|51499,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|6313",
